snippet.title: Astray - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Release trailer for our upcoming first-person horror/puzzle game, Astray.

The game is set in an abandoned museum based on unusual cultures, legends, and supernatural themes. But something more sinister lurks beneath the surface..

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/329200
Website: http://www.astray-game.com
